You'll be missed. My positive thoughts and wishes go with you. My your

just beyond your grasp, but which, if you will sit down
quietly, may alight upon you."

- Nathaniel Hawthorne, Author

----- Original Message -----
From: zenmomma2kids
To: unschooling-dotcom@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Thursday, June 12, 2003 5:07 PM
Subject: [Unschooling-dotcom] Gotta Go


Well it's time for me to log off from this list for awhile. We sold
our house at last and the move to Oregon is on in just 6 weeks! I
must force myself to STOP reading and start packing.

I hope to be back soon. I'll see you all in August at the conference.

Life is good.
~Mary, on the road again :o)


Good luck mary. Look forward to having you back when you are done.
Maureen
